task.summary: Added URDF folder and updated Ghost.urdf file to most recent version. Also added line that reads the current directory and locates the urdf locally so the code runs on all systems.
Made modifications to the gait. The robot now takes a list of 36 parameters to fully define the gait. I have also selected a hard coded set of parameters that make the robot move forward.
Created a robot class that holds the urdf path, parameters, and a fitness.
Updated Simulator class to work with robot class. Added reset feature to simulator, added mode attribute to robots.
Ran simulation for random and beam search. File names updated.
Created data plotting script and added videos of robot moving.
Added title, labels, and legend to learning curve plot.

Created Simulator class that creates two seperate simulations for the robot. One is for forward and inverse kinematics, the other is for rendering the robot visually for debugging. Created a leg trajectory generator and a leg cycle manager for commanding the legs of the robot. Running the main of the Trajectory Executor class will make the robot walk in simulation. The urdf was also updated
Added motor function to main loop
